snippet.title: Turpin House of Horrors:  Jennifer & Jordan Turpin Interview
snippet.description:
You can support this channel by donating here:
https://www.paypal.me/aimeesaurusrex

Tonight we will discuss the case of 13 siblings tortured, neglected, starved and abused.  In January of 2018 their escape from their horrific home and parents became a reality as one sibling found the courage to break free.  Recently, two of the siblings spoke w/ Diane Sawyer of 20/20.  Let's talk about that interview, and the aftermath of their foray into freedom. 

*** "Chadus Daybellus Hasus Nose Chinus." ~ ancient latin, unknown
